 I am happy to join with you today. Are we to go down in history? How's the greatest demonstration for freedom in the history of our nation? 5 score years ago Great American in whose symbolic Shadow We Stand today Find the Emancipation Proclamation. this momentous decree came out. as a grant Beacon Light Of Hope to millions of negro slaves. Who had been seared in the Flames of withering Injustice? It came out so joyous Daybreak. 2 in the long night of their captivity But one hundred years later. Gum negro steel is not free. one hundred years later the life of a negro is still sadly crippled by the manacles of segregation and the chains of discrimination. 